This directory should contain the following items:

- ewascatalog-studies.txt file
  contains metadata table from EWAS catalog
  obtained from:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/download/
  located under:  Download all meta-data
  exact address:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/static//docs/ewascatalog-studies.txt.gz

- ewascatalog-results.txt file
  contains results table from EWAS catalog
  obtained from:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/download/
  located under:  Download all results
  exact address:  https://www.ewascatalog.org/static//docs/ewascatalog-results.txt.gz
